f_n\uparrow 1_U
 f_n(x):=n\cdot d(x,U^c)\wedge 1,\quad n\geq 1. 
 \mu(U)=\int 1_U\,\mathrm d\mu=\lim_{n\to\infty}\int f_n\,\mathrm d\mu=\lim_{n\to\infty}\int f_n\,\mathrm d\nu=\nu(U). 
